headline: Interactive Brokers Expands Global Market Access with the Taipei Exchange
summary: GREENWICH, Conn., November 18, 2025--Interactive Brokers (Nasdaq: IBKR) announced access to the Taipei Exchange (TPEx), further expanding its global reach.
